Terms of Service - Shimo

Terms of service for the Shimo bot, this guides our clients on how they can use Shimo bot.

- Conditions
General conditions regarding Shimo bot are under this topic.

1. Our terms and conditions apply to each and every user of Shimo Bot.
2. By adding Shimo in your server, you agree to these terms of service and the future terms which we may add after a notice.

- Terms of Use

1. The client must not resell the premium codes.
2. Intentional command spam or attempts to crash the bot should not be made.
3. Shimo should not be used in Bot spam servers which cause command spam.
4. Shimo Team reserves the rights to prohibit any server or user from using Shimo.
5. The client is responsible for any violation caused by them.
6. We have the rights to update terms of service anytime with a notice in the support server.

- Terms of Use (Actions)
Shimo Team, reserves the rights to prohibit any user or any server from using actions feature if they fail to comply with our rules.

1. Servers must use an appropiate server name.
2. You must not use actions to harass people.
3. Ratelimits can be imposed on servers which cause overload on the backend of Shimo Bot.
4. Shimo team can delete any actions from a server which we may find inappropiate, they do not necessarily have to violate our rules.
5. Shimo team can prohibit a server from using Shimo bot for violating our rules or any other reason we might deem it necessary for.
